OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start for Shetland but
OL,6,Fcloudier with a few spots of light
OL,7,Frain at first for Orkney. Outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain will become more frequent for
OL,9,FOrkney in the afternoon, but Shetland
OL,10,Fwill be mostly dry until evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain for Orkney which
OL,14,Fwill spread across Shetland too.
OL,15,FBecoming rather misty into the early
OL,16,Fhours with further showery outbreaks
OL,17,Fof rain expected.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
