OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA rather cloudy and damp start
OL,6,Fto the morning with light and patchy
OL,7,Frain. Becoming drier through the day
OL,8,Fwith some bright or sunnier spells
OL,9,Fpossible in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMainly
OL,12,Fdry throughout this period. Some misty
OL,13,Flow cloud may linger at times,
OL,14,Fespecially on Tuesday but otherwise
OL,15,Flengthy sunny periods are expected.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
